It's actually not a joke.

00:04:32.060 --> 00:04:33.547
(Laughter)

00:04:35.700 --> 00:04:39.000
So today, we're delivering
about 20 percent

00:04:39.024 --> 00:04:41.262
of the national blood supply of Rwanda

00:04:41.286 --> 00:04:42.742
outside of Kigali.

00:04:43.339 --> 00:04:45.013
We serve about 12 hospitals,

00:04:45.037 --> 00:04:48.549
and we're adding hospitals to that network
at an accelerating rate.

00:04:48.573 --> 00:04:51.575
All of those hospitals only receive
blood in this way,

00:04:51.599 --> 00:04:55.830
and most of those hospitals
actually place multiple orders every day.

